snippet.title: Dark Mass - World Premiere Reveal Trailer | FGS LIVE FROM GDC
snippet.description:
A deep sea expedition goes tragically wrong in Dark Mass, a horror adventure from Path Games, in development for Xbox, PS5 and PC. The world premiere trailer was unveiled at FGS Live from GDC. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #darkmass #gdc
